{"id":232789528,"title":"懶人版 炊飯","content":"如題，真的超級懶\n這個食譜是我懶得煮菜的時候會做的\n給大家在懶懶的時候可以參考\n\n材料（2人份）\n海鮮。全聯一盒的量\n香菇。五朵\n白米。兩杯\n日式醬油。60cc（自己調整）\n高湯粉。一平匙\n\n步驟\n1.洗好米，水量比平時再少一點\n2.倒入醬油高湯粉攪拌\n3.將食材切好丟進去\n4.按下煮飯，等吃\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8fe09c95-5653-46db-ae2e-14698a8553eb/1280.jpeg\n\n所有的材料、調味料都可以自己調整\n水的部分如果喜歡吃軟一點的人\n就依照平常的量不用特別調整\n昨天試了雞肉跟玉米筍也很好吃喔😋","excerpt":"如題，真的超級懶，這個食譜是我懶得煮菜的時候會做的，給大家在懶懶的時候可以參考，材料（2人份），海鮮。全聯一盒的量，香菇。五朵，白米。兩杯，日式醬油。60cc（自己調整），高湯粉。一平匙，步驟，1.洗","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-30T09:06:58.161Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-30T09:07:36.014Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":140,"tags":[],"topics":["懶人","食譜"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"中原大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":138},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8fe09c95-5653-46db-ae2e-14698a8553eb/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"825ddb44-f3d1-4c3d-900f-6a61dea1298b","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8fe09c95-5653-46db-ae2e-14698a8553eb/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8fe09c95-5653-46db-ae2e-14698a8553eb/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8fe09c95-5653-46db-ae2e-14698a8553eb/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-30T09:06:58.161Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-30T09:07:36.014Z","width":640,"height":360},{"id":"825ddb44-f3d1-4c3d-900f-6a61dea1298b","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8fe09c95-5653-46db-ae2e-14698a8553eb/1280.jpeg","normali